ExpressRoute provides connectivity not only to Azure but also to Microsoft services like Microsoft 365 and Dynamics 365.

For example, organizations can access cloud applications securely without using the public internet.

# Real-Life Use Case
A real-life use case is enterprises accessing Microsoft 365 services with low latency.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is secure communication between business applications and cloud services.

This connectivity improves performance and security.
